     C           #SET11    BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD@RRN1     RRN1
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     X       30
      *
 B0  C           *IN80     DOWEQ*OFF
     C                     READ FCQPP32                  80
 B1  C           *IN80     IFEQ *OFF
